featured_reviews.review_id:
SURAH FATIHA (Roman Arabic & Roman Urdu Quran)

Bismi Allahi Ar-Rahmani Ar-Rahimi.
Al-Hamdu Lillahi Rabbi Al-`Alamina.
Ar-Rahmani Ar-Rahimi.
Maliki Yawmi Ad-Dini.
'Iyaka Na`budu Wa 'Iyaka Nasta`inu.
Ahdina As-Sirata Al-Mustaqima.
Sirata Al-Ladhina 'An`amta `Alayhim Ghayri Al-Maghdubi `Alayhim Wa La Ad-Dallina

01.01 ALLAH ke naam se jo bohat maherban bohat raham kerne wala

01.02 Sab tareef Allah Taalaa kay liye hai jo tamam jahanon ka palney wala hai.

01.03 Bara meharban nihayat reham kerney wala.

01.04 Badlay kay din (yani qayamat) ka maalik hai.

01.05 Hum sirf teri hi ibadat kertay hain aur sirf tujh hi say madad chahatay hain.

01.06 Humen seedhi (aur sachi) raah dikha.
01.07 Unn logon ki raah jin per tu ney inaam kiya unn ki nahi jin per ghazab kiya gaya aur nagumrahon ki.

Ameen

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
SURAH FATIHA (Roman Arabic & Roman Urdu Quran)

Bismi Allahi Ar-Rahmani Ar-Rahimi.
Al-Hamdu Lillahi Rabbi Al-`Alamina.
Ar-Rahmani Ar-Rahimi.
Maliki Yawmi Ad-Dini.
'Iyaka Na`budu Wa 'Iyaka Nasta`inu.
Ahdina As-Sirata Al-Mustaqima.
Arata Al-Ladhina 'An`amta `Alayhim Ghayri Al-MaghDubi `Alayhim Wa La AD-Dallina

01.01 The one who showed great mercy in the name of ALLAH

01.02 All praises are given to Allah Almighty who is the sustainer of the entire world.

01.03 Every kind hearted person has no mercy.

01.04 Change is the master of the day (i.e. doomsday).

01.05 We only worship you and we only say that we want help.

01.06 Show us the path of humanity (and truth).
01.07 The path of those people for whom you have rewarded and the path of those people for whom you have rewarded.

Ameen
